1
00:01:40,180 --> 00:01:44,800
=Love Story in the 1970s=

2
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:47,940
=Episode 1=

3
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:52,260
(Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory)
(April 1975)

4
00:01:52,980 --> 00:01:54,290
We're here!

5
00:01:54,404 --> 00:01:56,180
(Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory)
We're at the factory!

6
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,500
(Controlled Quality, Consistent Supply,
Strong Management, High Productivity)

7
00:01:57,500 --> 00:01:58,420
(Learn from the Daqing Spirit)

8
00:01:58,420 --> 00:01:59,380
(Promote Revolutionary Traditions
of Diligence and Hard Work)

9
00:01:59,380 --> 00:02:00,380
(Learn from Comrade Lei Feng)

10
00:02:00,930 --> 00:02:03,570
(On this sunny day,)

11
00:02:03,648 --> 00:02:04,626
(we're holding)

12
00:02:04,626 --> 00:02:07,330
(a friendly basketball match between
No. 2 Electromechanical Factory)

13
00:02:07,330 --> 00:02:08,610
(and No. 1 Textile Factory!)

14
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:12,730
(Their passion and spirit ablaze,)

15
00:02:12,730 --> 00:02:14,220
(and they are the epitome)

16
00:02:14,220 --> 00:02:17,982
(of unity, perseverance
and sportsmanship!)

17
00:02:19,570 --> 00:02:20,540
Morning, Mr. Qiu.

18
00:02:20,890 --> 00:02:21,610
Fei Ni.

19
00:02:22,026 --> 00:02:23,450
You look energetic with that flag.

20
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:30,340
(Let's give them a round of applause)

21
00:02:30,340 --> 00:02:33,130
(Fei Ni)
(to cheer for them!)

22
00:02:33,130 --> 00:02:34,290
(High Spirits)

23
00:02:34,290 --> 00:02:43,660
- Go!
- Go!

24
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:44,820
(Ms. Liu)
Ms. Liu.

25
00:02:45,170 --> 00:02:46,220
Why are you late?

26
00:02:46,220 --> 00:02:47,660
I went to get this.

27
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:49,130
What a huge flag!

28
00:02:49,130 --> 00:02:50,060
How is it?

29
00:02:50,060 --> 00:02:52,100
Not good, we're one point behind!

30
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:55,730
- Go!
- Go!

31
00:02:55,730 --> 00:02:56,410
Watch me.

32
00:02:57,220 --> 00:02:59,850
- Go!
- Go!

33
00:02:59,850 --> 00:03:02,030
Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory!

34
00:03:02,540 --> 00:03:04,400
(Ye Feng)
Never give up!

35
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,410
- Never give up!
- Never give up!

36
00:03:06,410 --> 00:03:07,893
We will win!

37
00:03:07,893 --> 00:03:09,540
- We will win!
- We will win!

38
00:03:09,540 --> 00:03:11,660
(Xu Hongqi)
Good work organizing this event, Ms. Xu.

39
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:13,170
Thank you, Sir.

40
00:03:13,170 --> 00:03:14,004
- Go!
- Go!

41
00:03:14,004 --> 00:03:15,871
(Combat Arrogance, Strive to Succeed)
Go! Go!

42
00:03:15,871 --> 00:03:16,980
- Go!
- Go!

43
00:03:16,980 --> 00:03:19,100
- Fight to win!
- Fight to win!

44
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:25,220
- Go!
- Go!

45
00:03:25,220 --> 00:03:28,570
- Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory!
- Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory!

46
00:03:28,570 --> 00:03:32,130
- Never give up!
- Never give up!

47
00:03:32,130 --> 00:03:34,300
- Electromechanical Factory!
- Electromechanical Factory!

48
00:03:34,315 --> 00:03:37,380
- Win the battle!
- Win the battle!

49
00:03:37,380 --> 00:03:39,850
Every point counts!

50
00:03:39,850 --> 00:03:44,340
- Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory!
- Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory!

51
00:03:44,340 --> 00:03:46,820
Electromechanical Factory!

52
00:03:46,820 --> 00:03:48,290
Never give up!

53
00:03:48,290 --> 00:03:50,410
Jiangcheng No. 1 Textile Factory!

54
00:03:50,410 --> 00:03:51,500
Win the battle!

55
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:53,410
We will win!

56
00:03:53,410 --> 00:03:55,100
(Textile VS Electromechanical)
Win the battle!

57
00:03:55,100 --> 00:03:57,060
Dunk every shot!

58
00:03:57,060 --> 00:04:16,250
- Go!
- Go!

59
00:04:20,700 --> 00:04:23,900
(Jilin-Jiangcheng)

60
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:26,720
Show your tickets.

61
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:32,670
Ticket, please.

62
00:04:33,410 --> 00:04:34,410
Need water?

63
00:04:35,290 --> 00:04:36,410
Watch your bags.

64
00:04:38,930 --> 00:04:39,930
Ticket, please.

65
00:04:47,140 --> 00:04:47,930
Ticket, please.

66
00:04:52,610 --> 00:04:54,020
- Here.
- Excuse me.

67
00:04:55,750 --> 00:04:57,010
Look.

68
00:04:57,980 --> 00:04:59,740
Look, it's a mountain.
You love mountains.

69
00:05:00,370 --> 00:05:01,730
What's on the mountain?

70
00:05:02,730 --> 00:05:04,690
(Fang Muyang)
Trees, rocks and birds.

71
00:05:04,900 --> 00:05:06,050
You see birds?

72
00:05:06,050 --> 00:05:07,410
How many can you see?

73
00:05:07,410 --> 00:05:07,920
Five.

74
00:05:09,050 --> 00:05:10,540
You saw five birds?

75
00:05:11,050 --> 00:05:12,410
So many?

76
00:05:13,730 --> 00:05:15,020
There's a river.

77
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:15,930
See?

78
00:05:16,370 --> 00:05:17,410
You like trains?

79
00:05:18,850 --> 00:05:19,930
Have some corn bread.

80
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:25,490
Look.

81
00:05:27,340 --> 00:05:29,580
When we reach Jiangcheng,
I'll buy you something tasty.

82
00:05:30,050 --> 00:05:31,660
What's good in Jiangcheng?

83
00:05:31,780 --> 00:05:32,780
Jiangcheng?

84
00:05:33,610 --> 00:05:34,709
We've got lots of good food.

85
00:05:34,710 --> 00:05:36,729
Ice cream and pork chops
at Deda Western Restaurant,

86
00:05:36,730 --> 00:05:38,020
lion's head meatballs
at Yuhua Restaurant,

87
00:05:38,020 --> 00:05:39,020
beef noodles at Shangcheng Street,

88
00:05:39,020 --> 00:05:40,410
and brown sugar pastries
at the train station.

89
00:05:40,410 --> 00:05:41,960
Just thinking about it makes me drool.

90
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,137
You're from Jiangcheng, too?

91
00:05:45,980 --> 00:05:46,780
Comrade.

92
00:05:47,660 --> 00:05:49,100
Why don't I sketch you two?

93
00:05:50,170 --> 00:05:52,220
For free.
Just give me a piece of corn bread.

94
00:05:54,610 --> 00:05:55,580
Are you an artist?

95
00:05:56,020 --> 00:05:56,810
Just a hobby.

96
00:05:57,250 --> 00:05:58,660
I've never had a portrait.

97
00:05:58,730 --> 00:06:00,071
Why don't we let him sketch us?

98
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:01,170
Sure.

99
00:06:01,170 --> 00:06:02,850
Comrade, draw nicely.

100
00:06:02,850 --> 00:06:05,460
Otherwise, we won't give you any bread.

101
00:06:05,460 --> 00:06:06,050
Sure.

102
00:06:15,410 --> 00:06:20,100
- Go!
- Go!

103
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:22,250
(Textile VS Electromechanical)
Go!

104
00:06:22,250 --> 00:06:29,020
- Go!
- Go!

105
00:06:39,671 --> 00:06:42,648
(Textile, 56 VS Electromechanical, 54)
Game over! Textile Factory wins!

106
00:06:59,340 --> 00:07:00,510
Great work.

107
00:07:01,540 --> 00:07:02,220
Congratulations.

108
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:03,170
Thank you, Sir.

109
00:07:07,730 --> 00:07:09,170
Ms. Liu, hold this for me.

110
00:07:09,170 --> 00:07:09,850
Sure.

111
00:07:16,540 --> 00:07:17,660
Nice performance.

112
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:18,580
Keep it up.

113
00:07:19,140 --> 00:07:20,340
Don't get arrogant, though.

114
00:07:20,490 --> 00:07:21,460
Relax, Mom.

115
00:07:21,930 --> 00:07:24,020
This year's city-level champion

116
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:25,715
will be Jiangcheng
No. 1 Textile Factory.

117
00:07:26,140 --> 00:07:26,930
Don't call me mom.

118
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:28,340
At the factory,

119
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:29,610
call me Ms. Xu.

120
00:07:29,730 --> 00:07:30,700
Okay.

121
00:07:30,730 --> 00:07:31,540
Ms. Xu.

122
00:07:32,050 --> 00:07:32,930
Ye Feng.

123
00:07:33,410 --> 00:07:34,220
Wipe your sweat.

124
00:07:37,370 --> 00:07:39,660
You helped the Textile Factory
win the match.

125
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:41,170
We ought to learn from you.

126
00:07:42,293 --> 00:07:43,700
I'm just doing what I should do.

127
00:07:46,610 --> 00:07:47,610
Comrades!

128
00:07:48,410 --> 00:07:49,290
Comrades!

129
00:07:51,540 --> 00:07:53,410
Excellent performance today!

130
00:07:53,980 --> 00:07:56,730
You have won an honor for our factory!

131
00:07:56,930 --> 00:07:57,610
Another thing.

132
00:07:57,610 --> 00:07:59,660
I've talked to the canteen,

133
00:07:59,660 --> 00:08:02,340
and they're serving braised meat today!

134
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:03,700
- Great!
- Great!

135
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:05,050
- Thank you, Ms. Xu!
- Thank you, Ms. Xu!

136
00:08:05,050 --> 00:08:06,050
Ms. Xu...

137
00:08:06,050 --> 00:08:07,980
We need you to take a look
at the promotional materials.

138
00:08:07,980 --> 00:08:08,310
Sure.

139
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:08,850
This way.

140
00:08:08,850 --> 00:08:09,420
(Wang Xiaoman)

141
00:08:11,590 --> 00:08:13,600
Comrade, are you from
the Textile Factory, too?

142
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:17,660
Have you finished using it?

143
00:08:23,290 --> 00:08:25,140
Yes, thank you.

144
00:08:37,420 --> 00:08:39,100
What can you see on the mountain?

145
00:08:39,530 --> 00:08:41,730
Grandma, I see boars.

146
00:08:42,340 --> 00:08:43,490
Birds and boars?

147
00:08:44,730 --> 00:08:45,610
Done.

148
00:08:45,850 --> 00:08:46,180
What...

149
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:47,060
That fast?

150
00:08:47,650 --> 00:08:48,770
It'd better be good.

151
00:08:54,130 --> 00:08:54,940
Well?

152
00:08:55,130 --> 00:08:56,850
This looks better than me in real life.

153
00:08:57,300 --> 00:08:58,100
No way.

154
00:08:58,715 --> 00:09:00,130
You look better than the drawing.

155
00:09:04,610 --> 00:09:05,180
Comrade.

156
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:06,370
Thanks.

157
00:09:09,580 --> 00:09:11,420
Kid, this is for you.

158
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:13,130
It's okay.

159
00:09:13,137 --> 00:09:14,420
We're reaching our station soon.

160
00:09:14,420 --> 00:09:15,580
I'll buy something for him.

161
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:16,820
Ma'am, just take it.

162
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:18,300
Don't let him go hungry.

163
00:09:19,610 --> 00:09:20,820
Say thank you.

164
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,490
Thank you.

165
00:09:22,850 --> 00:09:23,770
You're welcome.

166
00:09:23,770 --> 00:09:25,180
Thank you, young man.

167
00:09:25,180 --> 00:09:25,980
You're welcome.

168
00:09:28,250 --> 00:09:29,010
And this, too.

169
00:09:29,010 --> 00:09:29,460
Eat up.

170
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:30,730
This is for you.

171
00:09:35,130 --> 00:09:36,650
How pretty.

172
00:09:36,650 --> 00:09:37,420
Right?

173
00:09:37,420 --> 00:09:37,820
Yeah.

174
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:39,130
So realistic!

175
00:09:40,060 --> 00:09:42,460
He even drew the corn bread.

176
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:47,010
You are an artist.

177
00:09:47,660 --> 00:09:49,420
Nah, I'm just dabbling.

178
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:52,660
- It looks like me.
- Sketch me, too.

179
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:53,370
Sure.

180
00:09:54,130 --> 00:09:54,820
Okay.

181
00:09:56,490 --> 00:09:58,610
Comrade, your hat is skewed.

182
00:09:58,610 --> 00:09:59,980
Yes, to the right.

183
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:12,180
(Jiangcheng)

184
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:13,610
Comrades, we're here.

185
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:14,220
Come on.

186
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:16,180
Please disembark orderly.

187
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:19,250
Mind the gap.

188
00:10:19,250 --> 00:10:20,850
If you are carrying luggage,

189
00:10:20,850 --> 00:10:23,060
be sure to have it with you.

190
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:24,480
If you are traveling with children,

191
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,940
keep an eye on them

192
00:10:25,940 --> 00:10:27,100
and hold their hands.

193
00:10:27,490 --> 00:10:28,580
Disembark orderly.

194
00:10:28,580 --> 00:10:29,700
Safety first.

195
00:10:29,700 --> 00:10:30,580
(Fang Muyang.)

196
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:32,580
(The factory was busy
during Chinese New Year.)

197
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:33,850
(Everyone didn't go home.)

198
00:10:34,404 --> 00:10:35,693
(The busy period is just over.)

199
00:10:35,737 --> 00:10:37,893
(You're one of our best
role models in the mill.)

200
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:39,890
(You have been chosen to represent)

201
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:42,315
(everyone in the factory
to visit their families.)

202
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:47,900
(Jiangcheng)

203
00:11:01,610 --> 00:11:02,370
Quick!

204
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:04,010
Not so fast!

205
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:04,770
Don't sneak off!

206
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:06,700
Let's play there!

207
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:07,650
- Okay!
- Okay!

208
00:11:10,226 --> 00:11:11,340
Why do you keep sneaking off?

209
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:13,780
(10 Shengli Road)

210
00:11:15,340 --> 00:11:17,180
(10 Shengli Road, Jiangcheng
Sun Hongmei, Lin Xiuying's Mother)

211
00:11:18,890 --> 00:11:19,700
Hello.

212
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:21,130
Hello.

213
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:23,460
Are you Lin's mother?

214
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:24,700
Yes.

215
00:11:25,370 --> 00:11:26,250
Hello, ma'am.

216
00:11:26,460 --> 00:11:27,580
I'm Lin's colleague.

217
00:11:27,626 --> 00:11:28,515
My name is Fang Muyang.

218
00:11:29,460 --> 00:11:30,850
You're Fang?

219
00:11:30,850 --> 00:11:32,860
Lin often writes to me
that you've been good to him

220
00:11:32,860 --> 00:11:34,060
while working in the northeast.

221
00:11:34,060 --> 00:11:35,610
It's my job.

222
00:11:35,610 --> 00:11:37,300
I'm on family reunion leave.

223
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:39,610
Lin got these goods for you.

224
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:41,650
He wanted me to tell you

225
00:11:41,650 --> 00:11:42,970
to enjoy them.

226
00:11:42,970 --> 00:11:44,160
Oh, my.

227
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:46,620
You're on family leave,
and you're delivering for him?

228
00:11:46,620 --> 00:11:47,460
Have some water.

229
00:11:47,460 --> 00:11:48,430
Thank you, but no.

230
00:11:48,710 --> 00:11:50,060
I need to deliver more items.

231
00:11:50,060 --> 00:11:52,010
Okay, when you're done delivering,

232
00:11:52,010 --> 00:11:52,770
go home

233
00:11:52,770 --> 00:11:54,650
and visit your parents, okay?

234
00:11:58,300 --> 00:11:58,980
Okay.

235
00:11:59,130 --> 00:11:59,420
Okay.

236
00:12:00,300 --> 00:12:01,300
Okay, ma'am.

237
00:12:01,300 --> 00:12:02,250
I'm off.

238
00:12:02,980 --> 00:12:04,010
Bye, Fang.

239
00:12:04,010 --> 00:12:04,690
Goodbye.

240
00:12:06,650 --> 00:12:07,530
What a nice kid.

241
00:12:08,540 --> 00:12:13,300
(13 Xiangdong Road, Jiangcheng)

242
00:12:16,780 --> 00:12:26,740
(Jiangcheng No. 1
Textile Factory Office)

243
00:12:32,370 --> 00:12:34,570
Your thought report...

244
00:12:35,770 --> 00:12:37,690
It's well written.

245
00:12:37,770 --> 00:12:38,890
For the past year,

246
00:12:38,890 --> 00:12:41,580
I can see you've been working hard.

247
00:12:42,650 --> 00:12:43,300
Good job.

248
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:45,490
Keep up the good work.

249
00:12:45,980 --> 00:12:46,940
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

250
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:47,970
Tu.

251
00:12:48,290 --> 00:12:50,040
- Ms. Xu?
- We snapped lots of photos

252
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:51,840
at the basketball court earlier.

253
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,370
Tell the Publicity Division

254
00:12:53,604 --> 00:12:54,937
to print those photos

255
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:56,370
and pin them on the Publicity Board.

256
00:12:56,370 --> 00:12:57,320
Okay, I'm on it.

257
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,100
Go..

258
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:01,610
Zhang, how's the report
for the Secretary coming along?

259
00:13:02,180 --> 00:13:03,250
I'm working on it, Ms. Xu.

260
00:13:03,940 --> 00:13:05,270
Keep it up.

261
00:13:05,580 --> 00:13:06,300
Yes, ma'am.

262
00:13:07,650 --> 00:13:08,300
Ms. Xu.

263
00:13:09,204 --> 00:13:10,320
What else do you need?

264
00:13:11,770 --> 00:13:13,550
This is my university
application letter.

265
00:13:16,010 --> 00:13:18,580
(Application Letter)
Last year, you said that I lack

266
00:13:18,580 --> 00:13:20,250
collective consciousness, and I agree.

267
00:13:20,730 --> 00:13:22,850
I've taken your advice to heart,

268
00:13:22,850 --> 00:13:24,180
and I've been improving myself.

269
00:13:24,370 --> 00:13:27,010
This year, I've joined every group event

270
00:13:27,010 --> 00:13:28,420
in the factory.

271
00:13:28,580 --> 00:13:29,340
So,

272
00:13:29,730 --> 00:13:30,700
can the factory

273
00:13:30,700 --> 00:13:32,300
vouch for me this year?

274
00:13:34,850 --> 00:13:35,940
Fei.

275
00:13:36,300 --> 00:13:38,460
Personally, I'd love to vouch

276
00:13:38,460 --> 00:13:40,940
for your application to
the Worker-Peasant-Soldier University.

277
00:13:41,180 --> 00:13:42,460
But, as you know,

278
00:13:42,460 --> 00:13:43,700
university referrals are decided

279
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:45,890
by a poll among the factory leaders.

280
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,100
So, right now,

281
00:13:48,100 --> 00:13:49,440
what you should do

282
00:13:50,130 --> 00:13:51,940
is to work hard

283
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:53,370
and unite everyone.

284
00:13:53,740 --> 00:13:54,660
Got it, Ms. Xu.

285
00:13:55,010 --> 00:13:56,320
I will follow your orders.

286
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,100
Ms. Xu.

287
00:13:57,110 --> 00:13:57,915
Today's paper.

288
00:13:58,871 --> 00:13:59,530
Perfect timing.

289
00:13:59,530 --> 00:14:01,620
(Feng Lin)
Feng, tell Fei Ni

290
00:14:01,890 --> 00:14:04,250
what a university candidate

291
00:14:04,250 --> 00:14:05,610
should keep in mind.

292
00:14:08,730 --> 00:14:10,420
Actually, Fei Ni is considered

293
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:12,071
well-educated among the factory workers.

294
00:14:12,260 --> 00:14:14,990
However, education is not the key factor
in university applications.

295
00:14:15,004 --> 00:14:17,329
What candidates should do
is cut down on superficial work

296
00:14:17,330 --> 00:14:19,350
and align themselves
with the country's ideologies.

297
00:14:19,820 --> 00:14:20,730
Feng Lin.

298
00:14:20,850 --> 00:14:22,850
I've been doing that.

299
00:14:23,530 --> 00:14:25,340
I write thought reports every month.

300
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:27,300
(Jiangcheng Daily)

301
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:30,130
Let's see what you wrote.

302
00:14:31,300 --> 00:14:32,250
"Their eyes

303
00:14:32,250 --> 00:14:34,660
sparkle in a way that is unique
to the workers,

304
00:14:34,660 --> 00:14:36,090
full of clearity..."

305
00:14:36,090 --> 00:14:36,760
It's "clarity".

306
00:14:37,610 --> 00:14:38,700
Full of clarity.

307
00:14:38,740 --> 00:14:41,380
(Full of clarity)

308
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:48,940
This is your biggest problem.

309
00:14:49,010 --> 00:14:50,700
Your writing should be easily understood

310
00:14:50,700 --> 00:14:52,220
by the ordinary workers and farmers.

311
00:14:52,220 --> 00:14:54,100
You just had to use
these difficult words

312
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:57,060
to show that you're
more cultured than them, right?

313
00:14:57,180 --> 00:14:59,770
This proves that you look down on them.

314
00:14:59,770 --> 00:15:02,020
How is that being aligned
with the country's ideologies?

315
00:15:02,060 --> 00:15:04,150
No, Ms. Xu.

316
00:15:04,150 --> 00:15:05,340
I didn't.

317
00:15:11,610 --> 00:15:12,770
I think

318
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:16,060
Feng has a point.

319
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:18,260
Don't use difficult words.

320
00:15:18,260 --> 00:15:19,730
We need to cater

321
00:15:20,610 --> 00:15:21,650
to other comrades

322
00:15:21,890 --> 00:15:23,460
who are less educated.

323
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:26,220
You're right, Ms. Xu.

324
00:15:26,370 --> 00:15:27,340
I'll keep that in mind.

325
00:15:27,890 --> 00:15:28,280
Good.

326
00:15:29,130 --> 00:15:30,100
But, Ms. Xu.

327
00:15:30,610 --> 00:15:31,730
If I can go to university

328
00:15:31,730 --> 00:15:33,180
and learn further,

329
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:34,220
I'd certainly improve.

330
00:15:34,226 --> 00:15:36,130
What kind of place
do you think the university is?

331
00:15:36,130 --> 00:15:37,250
Everyone wants to improve.

332
00:15:37,250 --> 00:15:39,293
Does that mean everyone
gets to enter university?

333
00:15:39,804 --> 00:15:41,530
You got in
despite your vocabulary level,

334
00:15:41,530 --> 00:15:42,580
so why can't I?

335
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:43,240
What do you mean?

336
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:43,820
What I said.

337
00:15:43,820 --> 00:15:44,530
Say that again...

338
00:15:44,530 --> 00:15:45,340
That's enough.

339
00:15:47,420 --> 00:15:48,780
Your individualistic thoughts

340
00:15:49,426 --> 00:15:50,900
have not been fully eliminated.

341
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:52,940
You react too strongly

342
00:15:53,780 --> 00:15:55,300
towards criticism.

343
00:15:57,180 --> 00:15:58,850
Ms. Xu, I think her criticism is wrong.

344
00:15:58,850 --> 00:16:01,660
Does that mean she can't criticize you?

345
00:16:03,090 --> 00:16:06,210
If she's right, work on it.
If not, keep it in mind.

346
00:16:28,540 --> 00:16:29,570
It's okay, Sir.

347
00:16:30,410 --> 00:16:31,210
Fang.

348
00:16:31,490 --> 00:16:32,900
Join us for dinner.

349
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:33,970
Next time, Sir.

350
00:16:33,970 --> 00:16:34,450
Bye.

351
00:16:34,730 --> 00:16:35,260
See you.

352
00:16:35,430 --> 00:16:36,220
Stay safe.

353
00:16:41,700 --> 00:16:44,700
(44 Kangnan Road, Jiangcheng)

354
00:17:01,380 --> 00:17:05,300
(Humility Leads to Progress,
Pride Leads to Downfall)

355
00:17:15,620 --> 00:17:16,210
Fei Ni.

356
00:17:16,210 --> 00:17:16,730
You're back.

357
00:17:16,730 --> 00:17:17,200
Yeah.

358
00:17:17,290 --> 00:17:17,940
Hi, Ms. Wang.

359
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:20,730
Come on, make a move.

360
00:17:20,730 --> 00:17:23,030
Playing chess with you can be so vexing.

361
00:17:24,100 --> 00:17:24,820
Mr. Liu.

362
00:17:25,690 --> 00:17:26,770
(Mr. Liu)
Ni, you're back.

363
00:17:27,970 --> 00:17:28,490
Dad.

364
00:17:28,490 --> 00:17:29,180
(Fei Mingde)

365
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:31,600
The canteen was serving
braised meat today,

366
00:17:31,604 --> 00:17:32,471
so I got some for you.

367
00:17:33,380 --> 00:17:34,860
My daughter cares about me.

368
00:17:35,420 --> 00:17:36,660
Join me for a drink tonight.

369
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:37,900
No, thanks.

370
00:17:37,900 --> 00:17:38,660
I'm going back.

371
00:17:39,290 --> 00:17:40,100
Bye.

372
00:17:41,860 --> 00:17:42,480
Come on.

373
00:17:42,730 --> 00:17:43,420
Hurry up.

374
00:17:44,782 --> 00:17:45,715
Make a move, will you?

375
00:17:45,715 --> 00:17:47,310
You didn't ask me to join your drinking.

376
00:17:47,315 --> 00:17:49,450
Who cares, you're losing anyway.

377
00:17:54,940 --> 00:17:55,970
Ni, you're back.

378
00:17:57,530 --> 00:17:59,340
Ni, I'm borrowing your vinegar.

379
00:18:00,520 --> 00:18:01,020
Mom.

380
00:18:01,490 --> 00:18:02,070
I'm home.

381
00:18:02,582 --> 00:18:03,650
There's rice in the pot.

382
00:18:03,650 --> 00:18:04,710
Help yourself.

383
00:18:04,890 --> 00:18:05,660
I'm not hungry.

384
00:18:05,660 --> 00:18:06,700
I'm skipping dinner.

385
00:18:06,940 --> 00:18:11,340
(Wu Baoying)

386
00:18:18,960 --> 00:18:19,880
You scared me.

387
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:21,520
You didn't even make a sound.

388
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:25,180
Ni seems to be down and preoccupied.

389
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:29,850
She's submitting
her university application today.

390
00:18:31,090 --> 00:18:32,940
I guess she got rejected again.

391
00:18:34,810 --> 00:18:36,020
It's been four years.

392
00:18:36,020 --> 00:18:37,370
Does she still stand a chance?

393
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:39,020
Dad, Mom.

394
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:41,750
It's a small house.

395
00:18:42,180 --> 00:18:43,130
I can hear you.

396
00:18:47,340 --> 00:18:54,940
(15 April 1975)

397
00:18:55,020 --> 00:18:56,471
(44 Kangnan Road)
It's broken again?

398
00:18:56,500 --> 00:18:58,220
Yeah, the electric meter keeps ticking.

399
00:18:58,220 --> 00:18:58,900
Look.

400
00:19:07,940 --> 00:19:08,740
Stop!

401
00:19:11,700 --> 00:19:12,880
Nana, Jiang Xia!

402
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:13,660
Get back here!

403
00:19:13,870 --> 00:19:14,700
Don't run off!

404
00:19:15,170 --> 00:19:15,850
Get back here!

405
00:19:17,530 --> 00:19:18,180
Yang.

406
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:19,570
School's over?

407
00:19:20,090 --> 00:19:21,130
Wash your hands.

408
00:19:21,420 --> 00:19:23,260
(Tang Shutong)
I bought you ice cream.

409
00:19:23,850 --> 00:19:25,130
Thank you, Grandma.

410
00:19:25,130 --> 00:19:26,780
(Young Fang Muyang)

411
00:19:55,940 --> 00:19:56,560
Fang Muyang.

412
00:19:56,740 --> 00:19:58,700
Your parents have been sent
for re-education.

413
00:19:58,700 --> 00:20:00,290
You can't stay here anymore.

414
00:20:06,620 --> 00:20:09,020
(Young Fang Muyang)

415
00:20:28,570 --> 00:20:30,020
Comrade, who are you looking for?

416
00:20:32,610 --> 00:20:33,940
Wang Xiuju.

417
00:20:33,940 --> 00:20:34,980
Go in and turn right.

418
00:20:37,700 --> 00:20:38,330
Thank you.

419
00:20:52,180 --> 00:20:54,500
(University Plan: What I Need to Do)

420
00:20:54,700 --> 00:20:55,610
(Mr. Wang.)

421
00:20:55,610 --> 00:20:56,740
(Next week)

422
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:58,330
(marks my third year working here.)

423
00:20:58,330 --> 00:21:00,570
That means I'm eligible
for a university referral.

424
00:21:00,570 --> 00:21:01,330
(Three Years Ago)

425
00:21:01,330 --> 00:21:02,850
I don't care if you're one week

426
00:21:02,850 --> 00:21:04,610
or one day short.

427
00:21:04,610 --> 00:21:06,520
Young lady, you have
many future opportunities.

428
00:21:06,700 --> 00:21:08,050
Don't rush.

429
00:21:09,770 --> 00:21:10,570
Mr. Wang.

430
00:21:10,570 --> 00:21:11,700
(Two Years Ago)

431
00:21:11,700 --> 00:21:13,460
Have you looked at my application form?

432
00:21:13,460 --> 00:21:14,460
I've been working here

433
00:21:14,460 --> 00:21:16,290
for three years and 351 days.

434
00:21:16,290 --> 00:21:17,770
Work length is not a criterion.

435
00:21:18,570 --> 00:21:19,920
It's all about work capability.

436
00:21:20,026 --> 00:21:22,071
We'll talk when you win
a Technician Award.

437
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:25,290
(Technician Award Winners)

438
00:21:25,290 --> 00:21:27,404
(Fei Ni)
Ms. Xu, Mr. Wang mentioned

439
00:21:27,448 --> 00:21:29,500
(One Year Ago)
that if I win a Technician Award,

440
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:31,130
I'd get a university referral.

441
00:21:32,220 --> 00:21:33,130
As far as I know,

442
00:21:33,810 --> 00:21:36,530
you haven't been joining
group events this year.

443
00:21:36,530 --> 00:21:37,530
Fei Ni.

444
00:21:38,050 --> 00:21:39,980
Be a team player.

445
00:21:39,980 --> 00:21:41,940
University referrals are decided

446
00:21:41,940 --> 00:21:44,500
based on a voting process.

447
00:21:45,420 --> 00:21:46,050
(You seem to)

448
00:21:46,050 --> 00:21:47,130
(react too strongly)

449
00:21:48,090 --> 00:21:49,530
(against criticism.)

450
00:21:50,290 --> 00:21:51,610
(If she's right, work on it.)

451
00:21:51,610 --> 00:21:52,715
(If not, keep it in mind.)

452
00:22:05,020 --> 00:22:12,500
(Jiangcheng No. 2 Guesthouse)

453
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:13,130
Comrade.

454
00:22:13,570 --> 00:22:14,960
How much for a night's stay?

455
00:22:15,071 --> 00:22:16,420
Do you have a referral letter?

456
00:22:17,130 --> 00:22:17,700
Yes.

457
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:24,640
(This is to certify that Fang Muyang)

458
00:22:24,640 --> 00:22:25,340
(is visiting Jiangcheng
for family visitations.)

459
00:22:25,340 --> 00:22:25,940
(He should be granted staying rights.)

460
00:22:26,060 --> 00:22:27,799
It's 0.70 yuan
for a single room per night.

461
00:22:27,800 --> 00:22:29,160
How many nights are you staying?

462
00:22:29,940 --> 00:22:30,740
0.70 yuan?

463
00:22:34,500 --> 00:22:36,110
Zhang, we're off.

464
00:22:36,426 --> 00:22:37,900
There's no one else inside, right?

465
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:38,640
No.

466
00:22:38,980 --> 00:22:40,050
Good.

467
00:22:41,300 --> 00:22:44,130
(Dongfeng Bathhouse)

468
00:22:44,130 --> 00:22:45,130
Come early tomorrow.

469
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:56,100
(Warm Water)

470
00:23:57,770 --> 00:23:58,660
(Two yuan.)

471
00:23:58,660 --> 00:24:00,330
I'll buy it back in the future
at twice the amount.

472
00:24:00,330 --> 00:24:01,130
(Six Years Ago)

473
00:24:01,130 --> 00:24:03,090
(Young Fei Ni)
I can only pay one yuan.

474
00:24:03,370 --> 00:24:04,180
No deal, then.

475
00:24:04,420 --> 00:24:05,760
It's useless to you, anyway.

476
00:24:05,760 --> 00:24:07,190
You won't be using it.

477
00:24:07,382 --> 00:24:08,737
I'll sell it to the junk collector.

478
00:24:08,980 --> 00:24:10,700
Sure, go ahead.

479
00:24:10,980 --> 00:24:12,370
I'm sure no one else

480
00:24:12,370 --> 00:24:14,740
other than me would want that.

481
00:24:18,660 --> 00:24:19,740
No one wants it?

482
00:24:19,850 --> 00:24:20,770
I'll burn it, then.

483
00:24:21,040 --> 00:24:21,850
No.

484
00:24:24,260 --> 00:24:25,330
1.50 yuan.

485
00:24:26,130 --> 00:24:27,420
I can't go higher.

486
00:24:27,420 --> 00:24:29,530
I still need to buy lunch.

487
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:31,260
Deal.

488
00:24:34,460 --> 00:24:36,570
Anyway, I'm just leaving it
with you temporarily.

489
00:24:37,180 --> 00:24:38,700
I'll buy it back when I return.

490
00:24:40,660 --> 00:24:41,460
Fei Ni.

491
00:24:43,660 --> 00:24:44,610
I'm leaving tomorrow.

492
00:24:50,671 --> 00:24:53,248
Actually, it's good
that you're going away to work.

493
00:24:53,530 --> 00:24:56,020
You can go to many places
and see different scenery.

494
00:24:56,980 --> 00:24:59,460
Unlike me, who's never left Jiangcheng.

495
00:25:00,660 --> 00:25:01,460
It's okay.

496
00:25:01,604 --> 00:25:04,320
Wherever I go, I'll draw everything I see
so I can show you.

497
00:25:04,330 --> 00:25:05,500
No.

498
00:25:05,500 --> 00:25:07,530
You hid one of your sketches
in my Maths workbook,

499
00:25:07,530 --> 00:25:08,810
and I got a scolding.

500
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:10,370
I don't want your sketches.

501
00:25:16,850 --> 00:25:18,660
How long has it been since you last ate?

502
00:25:18,850 --> 00:25:19,980
Not that long ago.

503
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:21,500
Two or three days.

504
00:25:24,610 --> 00:25:25,330
Here.

505
00:25:25,330 --> 00:25:25,980
No.

506
00:25:25,980 --> 00:25:26,940
We made a deal,

507
00:25:26,940 --> 00:25:27,700
so 1.50 yuan it is.

508
00:25:29,020 --> 00:25:30,610
It's a loan. Remember to pay me back.

509
00:25:31,130 --> 00:25:31,940
Forget it.

510
00:25:32,137 --> 00:25:33,293
I guess you won't be able

511
00:25:33,293 --> 00:25:35,050
to repay the money you owe me.

512
00:25:35,093 --> 00:25:36,330
Just take care of yourself.

513
00:25:39,500 --> 00:25:39,940
Fei Ni.

514
00:25:43,700 --> 00:25:44,660
Wait for me.

515
00:25:46,980 --> 00:25:48,660
I'll pay twice as much back.

516
00:25:49,530 --> 00:25:51,130
Sure, it's a promise.

517
00:27:04,370 --> 00:27:05,500
Young lad.

518
00:27:07,610 --> 00:27:09,180
You really think

519
00:27:09,180 --> 00:27:10,570
you can hide yourself like this?

520
00:27:15,980 --> 00:27:16,770
Sir.

521
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:18,770
There's no one else here.

522
00:27:18,770 --> 00:27:20,180
Can you let me stay the night here?

523
00:27:21,090 --> 00:27:22,180
I'll leave in the morning.

524
00:27:22,180 --> 00:27:23,700
I can't.

525
00:27:24,460 --> 00:27:26,700
Who knows whether you're good or bad?

526
00:27:27,260 --> 00:27:29,050
Go, run along now.

527
00:27:29,050 --> 00:27:30,700
It's more comfortable to sleep at home.

528
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:34,020
I don't have a home.

529
00:27:34,500 --> 00:27:35,290
What...

530
00:27:37,090 --> 00:27:39,290
Still, you can't sleep here.

531
00:27:39,980 --> 00:27:41,260
This is a public space.

532
00:27:41,260 --> 00:27:42,940
If the higher-ups find out,

533
00:27:43,660 --> 00:27:44,940
I'd get punished.

534
00:27:45,330 --> 00:27:47,020
Fine, I'll leave.

535
00:27:49,610 --> 00:27:51,290
If you really have nowhere else to go,

536
00:27:51,570 --> 00:27:54,570
you can share a room with me tonight.

537
00:27:54,810 --> 00:27:57,220
I don't think your room
can fit another person.

538
00:27:58,420 --> 00:27:59,850
Beggars can be choosy, huh?

539
00:28:03,404 --> 00:28:04,530
I don't want to trouble you.

540
00:28:04,980 --> 00:28:05,980
The world is huge.

541
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:07,420
I'll find a place to sleep.

542
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:09,500
(Dongfeng Bathhouse)

543
00:28:09,500 --> 00:28:10,740
What a tall fellow.

544
00:28:11,137 --> 00:28:12,700
It's true, there's no room for him.

545
00:28:35,180 --> 00:28:36,610
(Fei Ni's house should be here.)

546
00:28:39,900 --> 00:28:40,980
(Which house is it?)

547
00:29:31,740 --> 00:29:34,660
Help! Building collapse!

548
00:29:35,220 --> 00:29:37,850
Ms. Liu's house has collapsed! Help!

549
00:29:38,570 --> 00:29:40,610
Help! Building collapse!

550
00:29:40,810 --> 00:29:42,850
Someone, help!

551
00:29:43,130 --> 00:29:44,700
Ms. Liu!

552
00:29:45,290 --> 00:29:46,500
Are you okay, Ms. Liu?

553
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:48,610
Quick, go save Ms. Liu!

554
00:29:48,770 --> 00:29:49,900
Where's my raincoat?

555
00:29:50,330 --> 00:29:51,900
Get me a flashlight.

556
00:29:51,900 --> 00:29:52,530
Okay.

557
00:29:52,850 --> 00:29:54,090
Dad, Mom, what happened?

558
00:29:54,090 --> 00:29:56,090
I heard someone cry for help.

559
00:29:56,090 --> 00:29:57,180
I'm going out.

560
00:29:57,180 --> 00:29:58,260
Stay at home, ladies.

561
00:29:58,260 --> 00:30:00,090
Be careful out there.

562
00:30:03,290 --> 00:30:03,740
Ms. Liu!

563
00:30:04,050 --> 00:30:04,810
What happened?

564
00:30:04,900 --> 00:30:05,740
My house collapsed!

565
00:30:05,900 --> 00:30:07,530
My husband and son are inside!

566
00:30:07,530 --> 00:30:08,330
Quick!

567
00:30:08,330 --> 00:30:09,290
Got them!

568
00:30:09,290 --> 00:30:10,980
- Get the cart!
- Maodou!

569
00:30:11,130 --> 00:30:11,810
Quick!

570
00:30:12,050 --> 00:30:13,230
Get the cart!

571
00:30:13,610 --> 00:30:14,130
Quick!

572
00:30:14,130 --> 00:30:14,940
Put him down!

573
00:30:15,330 --> 00:30:16,130
Help me!

574
00:30:16,130 --> 00:30:16,660
Careful!

575
00:30:16,980 --> 00:30:17,740
Hold tight.

576
00:30:18,330 --> 00:30:19,420
Maodou!

577
00:30:20,460 --> 00:30:22,930
- Hold tight!
- Hold tight!

578
00:30:22,960 --> 00:30:23,520
Go!

579
00:30:23,520 --> 00:30:24,220
Be careful!

580
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:25,330
Hurry up!

581
00:30:28,404 --> 00:30:29,850
All the houses here are in danger.

582
00:30:29,980 --> 00:30:31,260
A second collapse might happen.

583
00:30:31,500 --> 00:30:32,370
Get everyone out!

584
00:30:32,370 --> 00:30:33,050
Okay.

585
00:30:33,130 --> 00:30:34,530
- Quick!
- Quick!

586
00:30:35,050 --> 00:30:36,330
Get everyone out!

587
00:30:37,130 --> 00:30:37,940
Ms. Zhao!

588
00:30:38,090 --> 00:30:39,050
Come down!

589
00:30:39,050 --> 00:30:40,420
Your house is collapsing!

590
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:41,940
Ms. Liu!

591
00:30:42,770 --> 00:30:43,950
Ms. Liu, get out!

592
00:30:43,950 --> 00:30:45,360
- Ms. Liu!
- Wake up!

593
00:30:45,740 --> 00:30:46,050
Quick!

594
00:30:46,050 --> 00:30:46,530
Run!

595
00:30:46,530 --> 00:30:47,160
Quick!

596
00:30:47,520 --> 00:30:47,910
Go!

597
00:31:09,700 --> 00:31:10,370
Go!

598
00:31:15,570 --> 00:31:16,700
Someone help!

599
00:31:17,180 --> 00:31:18,460
Another house has collapsed!

600
00:31:19,130 --> 00:31:19,750
Feng Lin!

601
00:31:19,980 --> 00:31:20,910
Feng Lin!

602
00:31:21,500 --> 00:31:22,850
- Feng Lin!
- Hey!

603
00:31:22,850 --> 00:31:24,130
- Help!
- What's going on?

604
00:31:24,130 --> 00:31:26,320
This tree caused
Feng Lin's house to collapse.

605
00:31:26,320 --> 00:31:27,640
She is still inside!

606
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:28,240
I'll help!

607
00:31:29,050 --> 00:31:30,220
- Feng Lin!
- Feng Lin!

608
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:31,770
- Feng Lin!
- Feng Lin!

609
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:32,850
Feng Lin!

610
00:31:33,030 --> 00:31:33,590
Feng Lin!

611
00:31:33,610 --> 00:31:34,330
Feng Lin!

612
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:35,740
Feng Lin!

613
00:31:37,130 --> 00:31:38,050
Feng Lin!

614
00:31:39,420 --> 00:31:40,260
What should we do?

615
00:31:45,130 --> 00:31:45,700
Comrade!

616
00:31:46,130 --> 00:31:46,570
Comrade!

617
00:31:47,740 --> 00:31:48,290
(Wang Defa)

618
00:31:48,290 --> 00:31:48,940
What happened?

619
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,560
I'll do it!

620
00:32:11,337 --> 00:32:12,020
I can't do it.

621
00:32:12,020 --> 00:32:14,020
Get more people to help.

622
00:32:18,700 --> 00:32:19,420
Go!

623
00:32:19,900 --> 00:32:20,370
Go!

624
00:32:21,050 --> 00:32:21,530
Comrade.

625
00:32:21,850 --> 00:32:22,260
Save me.

626
00:32:22,740 --> 00:32:23,220
Comrade.

627
00:32:29,290 --> 00:32:29,980
Comrade.

628
00:32:29,980 --> 00:32:31,810
Save me. I don't want to die.

629
00:32:31,810 --> 00:32:32,980
Comrade.

630
00:32:33,330 --> 00:32:35,260
Comrade, save me. I don't want to die.

631
00:32:35,260 --> 00:32:35,900
Comrade.

632
00:32:35,900 --> 00:32:37,220
I don't want to die.

633
00:32:37,370 --> 00:32:38,020
You won't.

634
00:32:38,130 --> 00:32:39,180
Your leg is stuck.

635
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:45,260
Comrade.

636
00:32:45,271 --> 00:32:46,048
Here's a raincoat.

637
00:32:46,940 --> 00:32:47,330
Comrade.

638
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:49,130
What is it?

639
00:32:53,330 --> 00:32:53,850
Nothing.

640
00:32:54,180 --> 00:32:54,700
Thank you.

641
00:32:55,290 --> 00:32:55,900
You're welcome.

642
00:32:57,582 --> 00:32:58,500
I'll count to three.

643
00:32:58,560 --> 00:33:00,050
Pull your leg out as hard as you can.

644
00:33:00,420 --> 00:33:01,220
You hear me?

645
00:33:01,850 --> 00:33:02,330
One!

646
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:03,020
Two!

647
00:33:03,020 --> 00:33:03,500
Three!

648
00:33:07,980 --> 00:33:08,460
One!

649
00:33:08,460 --> 00:33:09,020
Two!

650
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:09,760
Three!

651
00:33:22,900 --> 00:33:24,420
Go!

652
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:32,160
Go!

653
00:33:38,640 --> 00:33:39,270
Quick!

654
00:33:39,330 --> 00:33:41,430
Another house has collapsed! Go!

655
00:33:41,700 --> 00:33:42,220
Run!

656
00:33:42,220 --> 00:33:43,330
Check if anyone's hurt!

657
00:33:43,530 --> 00:33:44,530
Where is he?

658
00:33:44,530 --> 00:33:45,210
Over there!

659
00:33:45,220 --> 00:33:46,050
He's still inside.

660
00:33:46,050 --> 00:33:47,330
Go now!

661
00:33:47,530 --> 00:33:47,900
Go!

662
00:33:48,420 --> 00:33:48,850
Go!

663
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:50,500
Quick!

664
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:51,937
Check if there's anyone else inside!

665
00:33:52,693 --> 00:33:53,500
That's a big tree.

666
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:55,048
Everyone should've evacuated by now.

667
00:33:56,760 --> 00:33:58,093
There's still someone inside!

668
00:33:58,330 --> 00:33:59,000
Save him!

669
00:33:59,090 --> 00:33:59,600
Quick!

670
00:33:59,600 --> 00:34:00,530
- Save him!
- Save him!

671
00:34:00,530 --> 00:34:01,170
Save him!

672
00:34:01,740 --> 00:34:02,190
Go!

673
00:34:02,330 --> 00:34:03,360
Comrade!

674
00:34:03,520 --> 00:34:04,010
Comrade!

675
00:34:20,380 --> 00:34:21,982
Last night's rain was hellish.

676
00:34:21,990 --> 00:34:23,900
- Homes were destroyed.
- Here, some warm water.

677
00:34:23,900 --> 00:34:24,420
Yes.

678
00:34:31,610 --> 00:34:32,410
Pull this out.

679
00:34:32,730 --> 00:34:33,250
Okay.

680
00:34:33,730 --> 00:34:34,250
Slowly.

681
00:34:34,500 --> 00:34:35,380
Be careful.

682
00:34:40,100 --> 00:34:42,380
(Jiangcheng Daily)

683
00:34:45,980 --> 00:34:46,730
Eat up.

684
00:34:46,730 --> 00:34:48,060
You can read later.

685
00:34:48,730 --> 00:34:50,570
I'm searching for news

686
00:34:50,570 --> 00:34:51,860
about the young man last night.

687
00:34:52,610 --> 00:34:53,770
News doesn't appear that fast.

688
00:34:54,610 --> 00:34:55,860
You don't know this,

689
00:34:55,860 --> 00:34:57,540
but that young man was godsent.

690
00:34:57,980 --> 00:35:00,610
When he saved Liu's family,

691
00:35:00,610 --> 00:35:02,060
he was already a hero.

692
00:35:02,250 --> 00:35:05,540
Then, he went back there

693
00:35:05,540 --> 00:35:07,170
to save more lives.

694
00:35:07,170 --> 00:35:08,570
What a pity.

695
00:35:09,250 --> 00:35:10,690
I thought he's in hospital?

696
00:35:10,690 --> 00:35:11,610
He didn't make it?

697
00:35:12,380 --> 00:35:13,650
How would I know?

698
00:35:14,130 --> 00:35:15,020
I heard

699
00:35:15,020 --> 00:35:17,610
his condition was serious, though.

700
00:35:19,690 --> 00:35:20,540
That young man

701
00:35:20,540 --> 00:35:21,860
was brave

702
00:35:21,860 --> 00:35:23,020
and dashing.

703
00:35:23,020 --> 00:35:24,860
(A Female Worker's Hymn of Love)

704
00:35:25,060 --> 00:35:25,540
Dad.

705
00:35:26,570 --> 00:35:28,170
Can you give me the paper?

706
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:29,650
Not now.

707
00:35:30,940 --> 00:35:31,770
Give her that.

708
00:35:32,860 --> 00:35:33,980
Ni wants to go to university.

709
00:35:33,980 --> 00:35:34,610
We subscribed to the daily

710
00:35:34,610 --> 00:35:36,760
so that she can keep herself
updated with current issues

711
00:35:36,760 --> 00:35:38,693
as well as the country's
policies and ideologies.

712
00:35:38,782 --> 00:35:40,610
It's not to satisfy
your hunger for gossip.

713
00:35:40,610 --> 00:35:42,020
You can read about that elsewhere.

714
00:35:42,020 --> 00:35:45,690
(A Female Worker's Hymn of Love.)

715
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:48,582
(For 20 years, a female worker
has been nursing a wounded hero.)

716
00:35:48,990 --> 00:35:53,020
(Now married, her dedication has also
won her a place in university.)

717
00:35:53,820 --> 00:35:54,940
The Secretary and I

718
00:35:54,940 --> 00:35:56,420
went to the hospital this morning.

719
00:35:57,170 --> 00:35:58,500
That young man

720
00:35:58,860 --> 00:36:00,540
is currently in stable condition.

721
00:36:01,210 --> 00:36:03,340
However, he did bump his head,

722
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:05,210
so there may be
a blood clot inside his brain.

723
00:36:05,380 --> 00:36:06,820
No one knows

724
00:36:07,690 --> 00:36:08,460
when he'll wake up.

725
00:36:09,210 --> 00:36:10,860
All his family members

726
00:36:11,250 --> 00:36:12,570
have been sent for re-education.

727
00:36:13,170 --> 00:36:14,650
We can't reach them for now.

728
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:16,650
I called you two over

729
00:36:16,650 --> 00:36:17,940
to discuss

730
00:36:18,420 --> 00:36:19,730
who we should send

731
00:36:20,540 --> 00:36:22,340
to take care of him.

732
00:36:24,060 --> 00:36:24,650
Ms. Xu.

733
00:36:25,020 --> 00:36:27,420
I know he saved my family,

734
00:36:27,420 --> 00:36:28,610
and I should go,

735
00:36:29,210 --> 00:36:31,940
but you know my family's condition.

736
00:36:31,940 --> 00:36:34,540
I have old folks and a kid to care for.

737
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:37,340
I can take care of him for a day or two,

738
00:36:37,860 --> 00:36:40,940
but as for the long term...

739
00:36:42,420 --> 00:36:45,130
As you can see, my arm is injured.

740
00:36:49,460 --> 00:36:50,250
Feng Lin?

741
00:36:56,460 --> 00:36:57,500
I...

742
00:37:01,460 --> 00:37:01,820
I...

743
00:37:01,820 --> 00:37:02,380
Ms. Xu!

744
00:37:04,730 --> 00:37:05,540
I'll go!

745
00:37:06,420 --> 00:37:07,290
Fei Ni?

746
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:08,570
Ms. Xu.

747
00:37:09,610 --> 00:37:12,250
I will take care of the hero
on behalf of our factory

748
00:37:12,250 --> 00:37:13,650
until he fully recovers.

749
00:37:13,650 --> 00:37:14,650
Trust me.

750
00:37:18,380 --> 00:37:19,460
Great!

751
00:37:20,060 --> 00:37:23,060
This is the perfect proletariat spirit!

752
00:37:26,610 --> 00:37:27,540
Fei.

753
00:37:28,130 --> 00:37:29,090
Do a good job.

754
00:37:29,380 --> 00:37:30,900
When the hero recovers,

755
00:37:31,290 --> 00:37:33,690
you will become our role model.

756
00:37:34,671 --> 00:37:36,190
I will make everyone in the factory,

757
00:37:36,220 --> 00:37:38,060
no, everyone in the industry,

758
00:37:38,210 --> 00:37:39,340
learn from you!

759
00:37:39,537 --> 00:37:40,900
You can count on me, Ms. Xu!

760
00:37:42,340 --> 00:37:43,060
Good.

761
00:37:50,420 --> 00:37:54,060
(Jiangcheng Worker-Peasant Hospital)

762
00:37:54,060 --> 00:37:55,420
(Keep Quiet)

763
00:38:01,770 --> 00:38:02,880
I'll write an article

764
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:04,410
about the hero later.

765
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:31,570
Which daily are you from?

766
00:38:32,540 --> 00:38:34,280
The patient needs to rest.

767
00:38:34,540 --> 00:38:36,460
You're affecting our work.

768
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:38,170
I'm not a reporter.

769
00:38:38,540 --> 00:38:41,170
I was sent by the Textile Factory
to tend to the hero.

770
00:38:43,315 --> 00:38:45,426
At least your factory's
still got some conscience.

771
00:38:45,730 --> 00:38:46,860
It's good that you're here.

772
00:38:47,090 --> 00:38:48,340
It's been rowdy in here.

773
00:38:48,340 --> 00:38:49,848
Reporters have been coming in and out.

774
00:38:49,871 --> 00:38:50,690
How annoying.

775
00:38:50,900 --> 00:38:51,730
Miss.

776
00:38:52,090 --> 00:38:53,570
When will he wake up?

777
00:38:53,860 --> 00:38:55,500
I can't say for sure.

778
00:38:55,610 --> 00:38:56,650
What's his name?

779
00:38:56,900 --> 00:38:57,860
Fang Muyang.

780
00:38:59,730 --> 00:39:00,460
Fang Muyang?

781
00:39:07,671 --> 00:39:09,250
(Six Years Ago)
Sell it to me for 0.03 yuan.

782
00:39:09,250 --> 00:39:10,900
It wasn't easy catching this housefly.

783
00:39:10,900 --> 00:39:11,610
0.05 yuan.

784
00:39:11,610 --> 00:39:13,340
That's crazy. 0.03 yuan. Hand it over.

785
00:39:13,340 --> 00:39:14,290
0.05 yuan.

786
00:39:14,290 --> 00:39:15,604
0.04 yuan, tops. Hand it over.

787
00:39:15,671 --> 00:39:16,830
0.05 yuan, and I mean it.

788
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:20,090
Fine, 0.05 yuan.

789
00:39:20,230 --> 00:39:20,940
Deal.

790
00:39:28,500 --> 00:39:29,610
Fang Muyang, are you nuts?

791
00:39:29,610 --> 00:39:30,880
Why are you stealing from her?

792
00:39:31,130 --> 00:39:32,130
I'm buying from her.

793
00:39:34,540 --> 00:39:36,420
Fei Ni, say goodbye to my money.

794
00:39:38,210 --> 00:39:39,820
Who are you?

795
00:39:39,820 --> 00:39:41,900
Kids, let me introduce someone new.

796
00:39:42,090 --> 00:39:42,940
He's joining us

797
00:39:42,940 --> 00:39:44,420
as a repeating student.

798
00:39:44,420 --> 00:39:45,610
His name is Fang Muyang.

799
00:39:45,610 --> 00:39:46,570
Starting from today,

800
00:39:46,570 --> 00:39:48,460
he's part of our class.

801
00:39:48,460 --> 00:39:50,060
Let's welcome him.

802
00:39:51,980 --> 00:39:52,650
Fang Muyang.

803
00:39:53,010 --> 00:39:54,380
(Chen Wenshu)
Sit beside Fei Ni.

804
00:39:57,730 --> 00:39:59,770
Let's begin today's class.

805
00:39:59,860 --> 00:40:01,170
Yesterday, we read the first part

806
00:40:01,170 --> 00:40:02,650
of Musings on the Red Cliff.

807
00:40:02,650 --> 00:40:03,982
We're actually sitting together.

808
00:40:04,980 --> 00:40:06,000
Okay, everyone.

809
00:40:06,540 --> 00:40:09,150
Open your textbooks. Let's continue.

810
00:40:23,990 --> 00:40:25,560
Fei Ni fell on the floor!

811
00:40:28,460 --> 00:40:29,420
Quiet!

812
00:40:29,650 --> 00:40:31,130
What are you doing, Fei Ni?

813
00:40:31,460 --> 00:40:32,860
Yelling in my class?

814
00:40:32,860 --> 00:40:34,130
You have no discipline.

815
00:40:34,130 --> 00:40:35,290
Meet me in my office later.

816
00:40:36,130 --> 00:40:37,130
Yes, ma'am.

817
00:40:47,210 --> 00:40:47,980
Fei Ni.

818
00:40:48,071 --> 00:40:49,500
You finished your reflection report?

819
00:40:49,690 --> 00:40:50,730
Did Ms. Chen lecture you?

820
00:40:51,770 --> 00:40:52,210
Let's go.

821
00:40:52,900 --> 00:40:53,900
I'll take you home.

822
00:40:54,290 --> 00:40:55,170
No need.

823
00:40:57,420 --> 00:40:58,980
I didn't mean to scare you.

824
00:40:59,048 --> 00:41:00,490
I just wanted to return the housefly.

825
00:41:01,471 --> 00:41:02,980
Who knew you'd be so timid.

826
00:41:05,770 --> 00:41:07,980
It's my fault. I'm sorry.

827
00:41:08,980 --> 00:41:10,340
I'll give you a ride back.

828
00:41:10,340 --> 00:41:11,570
You're limping.

829
00:41:11,570 --> 00:41:13,204
It'd be dark by the time you get home.

830
00:41:14,980 --> 00:41:17,210
Give me a chance to redeem myself, okay?

831
00:41:21,140 --> 00:41:25,220
(Jiangcheng No. 2 Secondary School)

832
00:41:32,271 --> 00:41:33,460
I'm good at cycling, right?

833
00:41:33,460 --> 00:41:34,540
Eyes on the road.

834
00:41:34,540 --> 00:41:35,820
You still don't believe me?

835
00:41:38,290 --> 00:41:39,340
I can even do this.

836
00:41:39,340 --> 00:41:40,970
Okay, I believe you.

837
00:41:47,860 --> 00:41:48,900
I'll pay for your shirt.

838
00:41:48,900 --> 00:41:49,900
No need.

839
00:41:49,900 --> 00:41:51,500
Just stay away from me.

840
00:42:12,460 --> 00:42:13,260
(No way.)

841
00:42:13,730 --> 00:42:15,420
(It's bad luck every time I see you.)

842
00:42:15,570 --> 00:42:16,290
(I quit.)

843
00:42:22,580 --> 00:42:23,920
(A Female Worker's Hymn of Love)

844
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:25,120
(For 20 years, a female worker
has been nursing a wounded hero.)

845
00:42:25,120 --> 00:42:26,220
(Now married, her dedication
has also won her a place in university.)

846
00:42:29,420 --> 00:42:30,210
Fang Muyang.

847
00:42:31,540 --> 00:42:33,950
As long as I take good care of you,

848
00:42:34,290 --> 00:42:37,130
I might get picked as a role model.

849
00:42:37,250 --> 00:42:39,130
When I become a role model,

850
00:42:39,130 --> 00:42:40,540
they'd have no reason

851
00:42:40,540 --> 00:42:42,020
to deny my university referral.

852
00:42:48,130 --> 00:42:49,130
Fang Muyang.

853
00:42:49,820 --> 00:42:52,130
You got me into trouble so many times.

854
00:42:52,250 --> 00:42:53,060
This time,

855
00:42:53,460 --> 00:42:55,540
you have to make it up to me.

856
00:42:55,540 --> 00:42:57,500
Wake up soon,

857
00:42:57,500 --> 00:43:00,290
and I'll write everything off.

858
00:43:00,290 --> 00:43:01,730
We'll be even, okay?

859
00:43:06,090 --> 00:43:07,090
Silence is consent.

860
00:43:07,090 --> 00:43:08,570
That's settled, then.

861
00:43:09,900 --> 00:43:11,020
Let's work hard together.

862
00:43:11,460 --> 00:43:12,500
Old friend.

863
00:43:28,860 --> 00:43:33,340
♪After the laughter, I think of you♪

864
00:43:35,900 --> 00:43:40,620
♪After the storm, I think of you♪

865
00:43:43,140 --> 00:43:49,260
♪In the little courtyard,
there you are dancing♪

866
00:43:50,260 --> 00:43:54,820
♪That earnest you,
smiling so innocently♪

867
00:43:57,300 --> 00:44:02,060
♪In spring, I stay by your side♪

868
00:44:04,500 --> 00:44:08,860
♪When summer comes, I watch over you♪

869
00:44:11,220 --> 00:44:17,860
♪In the light of dawn, you belong to me♪

870
00:44:17,860 --> 00:44:27,460
♪At the edge of the world,
I will still hold you tight♪

871
00:44:28,540 --> 00:44:34,700
♪There is a small place♪

872
00:44:34,700 --> 00:44:41,500
♪Where they carry big dreams♪

873
00:44:41,500 --> 00:44:48,860
♪Every lovely face♪

874
00:44:49,740 --> 00:44:55,900
♪Shines brightly in the heart♪

875
00:44:56,700 --> 00:45:02,740
♪Even when we collide,
we hold our course♪

876
00:45:03,940 --> 00:45:09,740
♪Even when we stumble,
we keep our resolve♪

877
00:45:10,820 --> 00:45:17,100
♪My you, walking toward the distance♪

878
00:45:17,900 --> 00:45:26,140
♪Please carry our dreams
and let them soar♪
